Senate Resolution 75
By: Senators Anderson of the 24th, Burns of the 23rd, Hickman of the 4th, Jones II of the
22nd, Williams of the 25th and others
A RESOLUTION
1 Congratulating the Harlem High School Bulldogs baseball team for winning the 2024 GHSA
2 Class AAA State Baseball Championship; and for other purposes.
3 WHEREAS, the Harlem High School Bulldogs baseball team has established and maintained
4 a proud tradition of excellence with equal emphases on character and academics; and
5 WHEREAS, this superlative team completed its triumphant season of baseball competition
6 by posting an outstanding record of 38 wins and only one loss; and
7 WHEREAS, the team brought special recognition to its school and to Columbia County by
8 winning the 2024 GHSA Class AAA State Baseball Championship; and
9 WHEREAS, as further testament to their exemplary performance, the Harlem High School
10 Bulldogs baseball team earned a No. 1 ranking across all classifications in the State of
11 Georgia as well as a No. 9 ranking in the nation; and
12 WHEREAS, this championship victory marks the seventh state championship under the
13 guidance of Head Coach Jimmie Lewis, who now has more than 900 career wins; and
